alice.util

Class ReadOnlyLinkedList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • alice.util.ReadOnlyLinkedList<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, List<E>

    public class ReadOnlyLinkedList<E>
extends Object
implements List<E>
    ReadOnlyLinkedList encapsulate a LinkedList and ensures that the given list is navigated only. Even if ReadOnlyLinkedList implements List it doesn't support modifiers methods, and throws UnsupportedOperationException if invoked.
    Since:
    2.2
    Author:
    Paolo Contessi
